E-10 INPUT WIRE DATA.
E-11 INPUT WIRE DIAMETER DATA.
E-12 INPUT PARTS CDOE IS DIFFERENT.
E-13 THIS IS NOT IN  DETAIL MASTER FILE.
E-14 INPUT NUMBER OF KANBAN.
** UP1/UP2
00-DELETE
11-CHANGE
22-ADDITION
